Title: Bring It On: Again
Writer: Claudia Grazioso (story), Claudia Grazioso (screenplay), Brian Gunn (screenplay), Mark Gunn (screenplay)
Actors: Anne Judson-Yager, Bree Turner, Kevin Cooney, Faune Chambers Watkins
Plot: When new students can't get onto their college cheerleading team, they form their own squad and prepare for a cheer off.
